questions.scenario:
You are debugging a production issue where a high-throughput Spring Boot microservice is experiencing a gradual increase in Metaspace usage, eventually resulting in a `java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Metaspace` after 12 hours of uptime. You trace the issue to this service class:

java
@Service
public class ReportService {
    @Autowired
    private ApplicationContext context;

    public void generateDynamicReport(ReportConfig config) {
        ProxyFactory factory = new ProxyFactory(new ReportProcessorImpl());
        factory.addAdvice(new TransactionInterceptor(
            context.getBean(PlatformTransactionManager.class), 
            new DefaultTransactionAttribute()
        ));
        ReportProcessor proxy = (ReportProcessor) factory.getProxy();
        proxy.process(config);
    }
}
